<h1>Open Seas</h1>
<p>Open Seas is a massively multiplayer online web browser game set in the time of swashbuckling and sailing the high seas. Players can navigate a customized ship with a personalized captain while exploring the different regions of Open Seas world. They can choose to trade, pillage, or protect and their actions determine their future career. Shall they be tired of the adventurous life on the Open Seas, players can choose to sit at port and grab a swig of rum with their fellow seamen. With Open Seas' easily understood interface and low computer requirements, anyone can play with an internet connection. A player controlled economy and endless amounts of sea maybe a pirate's life is for you.</p>
